Meet <b>Jake</b> our featured citizen of the week!<br><br>Jake has been holding down the fort at <a href='/home/?user=mtbiker101112'>12164-C Thunderbird Place</a> residence in Ravenwood.  <br><br>He's only been living there since July 28th, 2008. He loves the old historic architecture and majestic views of downtown Millsberry that the neighborhood is known for. <br><br>If you live in the neighborhood, be sure to welcome Jake into the community.<br><br>Jake describes himself as friendly, a little athletic, and creative. He'll most likely greet you with a hearty "hello". Chances are he'll follow with a joke. And it's sure to be a side-splitter.  <br><br>When he's not playing sports like Basketball, Jake enjoys music. The Recording Studio must be right up his alley. <br><br>Jake's favorite colors are violet, yellow, and silver. That seems to be the perfect color combination for an awesome basketball jersey. Coincidence? We think not. <br><br>Next time you see Jake, welcome him to Millsberry, and thank him for being such a great citizen!</div>
